concentric conducting spherical shells
of radii \( a \) and \( b(a<b) . \) The inner shell is

difference between the shells is given
by \( \boldsymbol{V}_{\boldsymbol{i}}-\boldsymbol{V}_{\mathbf{0}}=-\int_{\boldsymbol{b}}^{\boldsymbol{a}} \boldsymbol{E} \boldsymbol{d} \boldsymbol{r} \)

\( \Rightarrow V=\frac{Q(b-a)}{4 \pi \varepsilon_{o} a b} \)
